OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDriver shortage: 50,000    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore HGV driving tests     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpromised a year            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has confirmed plans to  
OL,6, speed up the process of obtaining an   
OL,7, HGV driver licence, amid a nationwide  
OL,8, shortage of drivers.                   
OL,10,FUp to 50,000 more HGV driving tests    
OL,11,Fwill be made available each year by    
OL,12,Fshortening the application process and 
OL,13,Fthe tests themselves, it said.         
OL,15,FThe UK faces a shortfall of around     
OL,16,F90,000 drivers, which has hit the      
OL,17,Fsupply of food, petrol and other goods.
OL,19,FHowever, industry groups said the new  
OL,20,Fplans did not go far enough.           
